ISLAMABAD, Mar 26 (APP): Senate Chairman Muhammad Sadiq Sanjrani has declared Syed Yousuf RazaÂ  Gillani as leader of the opposition in the Senate with effect from March 26.
The chairman declared Yousuf Raza Gilani as leader of the opposition, in pursuance of Rule 16 (3) of the Rules of Procedure and Conduct of Business in the Senate 2012, said a notification issued here on Friday.
